data.description: Discover this charming 3-bed, 1.5-bath, 2 car garage brick ranch home nestled on a half-acre of land. Located in a tranquil neighborhood, this property offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and peaceful surroundings. Original hardwood floors throughout.  The living room has abundant natural light, thanks to large windows.  The kitchen has been recently updated and has modern style.  The back yard is expansive and full of possibilities.  Come see this classic brick ranch for yourself!
